com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util.Settings

  • public final class Settings
extends Object
    This configuration class accesses all values that are read from a settings file in plain text. The settings file cannot be modified at runtime, so the Settings class is effectively immutable.
    Author:
    Florian J. Breunig
